{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012LZCLUqJDzXtwNmiH6cV3c","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→## Codebase Patterns\n     2→- TypeScript source in `src/`, compiled to `lib/` via `tsc`, then bundled to `dist/` via `ncc`\n     3→- Build pipeline: `tsc && ncc build lib/index.js -o dist`\n     4→- `dist/index.js` must be committed (required by GitHub Actions runtime)\n     5→- `lib/` is gitignored (intermediate build output)\n     6→- ESLint configured with `@typescript-eslint/parser` and `@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin`\n     7→- Jest configured with `--passWithNoTests` flag\n     8→- All stage handlers are in `src/stages/` as default exports\n     9→- Shared types in `src/types.ts` (KilnContext, StageResult, KilnConfig, Octokit)\n    10→- `action.yml` uses `node24` runtime\n    11→- Only `anthropic_api_key` is a required input; others have defaults\n    12→\n    13→## 2026-03-01 - US-001\n    14→- Converted project from JavaScript to TypeScript\n    15→- Set up TypeScript build pipeline: tsc → ncc → dist/\n    16→- Updated action.yml to use node24 and datashaman author\n    17→- Created .eslintrc.json for TypeScript linting\n    18→- Added tsconfig.json with strict mode\n    19→- Files changed:\n    20→  - action.yml (node20 → node24, author fix)\n    21→  - package.json (TypeScript deps, build scripts, lint script)\n    22→  - tsconfig.json (new)\n    23→  - .eslintrc.json (new)\n    24→  - .gitignore (added /lib/, removed /dist/)\n    25→  - src/types.ts (new - shared type definitions)\n    26→  - src/index.ts (converted from .js)\n    27→  - src/router.ts (converted from .js)\n    28→  - src/config.ts (converted from .js)\n    29→  - src/labels.ts (converted from .js)\n    30→  - src/claude.ts (converted from .js)\n    31→  - src/stages/*.ts (all 7 stages converted from .js)\n    32→  - dist/index.js (rebuilt)\n    33→- **Learnings for future iterations:**\n    34→  - The project uses `@actions/core` and `@actions/github` for GitHub Actions integration\n    35→  - The Octokit type is `InstanceType<typeof GitHub>` from `@actions/github/lib/utils`\n    36→  - Context type is from `@actions/github/lib/context`\n    37→  - `deepMerge` in config.ts needs explicit `unknown` casting to bridge between `KilnConfig` and `Record<string, unknown>`\n    38→  - GitHub Actions requires `dist/` to be committed for the action to work\n    39→---\n    40→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"942cf364-60e4-40c3-bc94-9e511a2c0dff","uuid":"9c86f5fd-ba28-4bb1-bfde-d67fa0c3c7dd","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/marlinf/Projects/datashaman/kiln-action/.chief/prds/main/progress.md","content":"## Codebase Patterns\n- TypeScript source in `src/`, compiled to `lib/` via `tsc`, then bundled to `dist/` via `ncc`\n- Build pipeline: `tsc && ncc build lib/index.js -o dist`\n- `dist/index.js` must be committed (required by GitHub Actions runtime)\n- `lib/` is gitignored (intermediate build output)\n- ESLint configured with `@typescript-eslint/parser` and `@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin`\n- Jest configured with `--passWithNoTests` flag\n- All stage handlers are in `src/stages/` as default exports\n- Shared types in `src/types.ts` (KilnContext, StageResult, KilnConfig, Octokit)\n- `action.yml` uses `node24` runtime\n- Only `anthropic_api_key` is a required input; others have defaults\n\n## 2026-03-01 - US-001\n- Converted project from JavaScript to TypeScript\n- Set up TypeScript build pipeline: tsc → ncc → dist/\n- Updated action.yml to use node24 and datashaman author\n- Created .eslintrc.json for TypeScript linting\n- Added tsconfig.json with strict mode\n- Files changed:\n  - action.yml (node20 → node24, author fix)\n  - package.json (TypeScript deps, build scripts, lint script)\n  - tsconfig.json (new)\n  - .eslintrc.json (new)\n  - .gitignore (added /lib/, removed /dist/)\n  - src/types.ts (new - shared type definitions)\n  - src/index.ts (converted from .js)\n  - src/router.ts (converted from .js)\n  - src/config.ts (converted from .js)\n  - src/labels.ts (converted from .js)\n  - src/claude.ts (converted from .js)\n  - src/stages/*.ts (all 7 stages converted from .js)\n  - dist/index.js (rebuilt)\n- **Learnings for future iterations:**\n  - The project uses `@actions/core` and `@actions/github` for GitHub Actions integration\n  - The Octokit type is `InstanceType<typeof GitHub>` from `@actions/github/lib/utils`\n  - Context type is from `@actions/github/lib/context`\n  - `deepMerge` in config.ts needs explicit `unknown` casting to bridge between `KilnConfig` and `Record<string, unknown>`\n  - GitHub Actions requires `dist/` to be committed for the action to work\n---\n","numLines":40,"startLine":1,"totalLines":40}}}
