{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01297XPNwSjJujYuqDmKkibP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"US-004 is complete. There are still stories with `passes: false` (US-005 through US-018), so another iteration will pick up the next story.\n\n**Summary of US-004 — Claude Code Action Integration Layer:**\n\n- Refactored `src/claude.ts` into a proper integration layer with `invokeClaude()` as the primary utility\n- **AC1**: Accepts prompt (string), API key, and optional config (`ClaudeConfig` with timeoutMinutes, allowEdits, octokit, context)\n- **AC2**: Invokes Claude Code CLI (the same mechanism claude-code-action uses internally)\n- **AC3**: Returns structured `ClaudeResult` with output, success boolean, and optional error\n- **AC4**: Defaults to 30-minute timeout (matching v1); detects killed processes for specific timeout error messages\n- **AC5**: Posts branded error comments on issues/PRs when octokit+context are provided; best-effort (won't crash if comment posting fails)\n- **AC6**: API key passed only via `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` env var (never in command string); redacted from error comments via `sanitizeOutput()`\n- 29 new tests covering all acceptance criteria\n- All 76 tests passing, typecheck and lint clean"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":311,"cache_read_input_tokens":73238,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":311},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cab57a4f-e8df-4648-9c51-7e23a35b2ad7","uuid":"11570385-5a90-4453-91ed-684bdb9690e4"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":479414,"duration_api_ms":491326,"num_turns":54,"result":"US-004 is complete. There are still stories with `passes: false` (US-005 through US-018), so another iteration will pick up the next story.\n\n**Summary of US-004 — Claude Code Action Integration Layer:**\n\n- Refactored `src/claude.ts` into a proper integration layer with `invokeClaude()` as the primary utility\n- **AC1**: Accepts prompt (string), API key, and optional config (`ClaudeConfig` with timeoutMinutes, allowEdits, octokit, context)\n- **AC2**: Invokes Claude Code CLI (the same mechanism claude-code-action uses internally)\n- **AC3**: Returns structured `ClaudeResult` with output, success boolean, and optional error\n- **AC4**: Defaults to 30-minute timeout (matching v1); detects killed processes for specific timeout error messages\n- **AC5**: Posts branded error comments on issues/PRs when octokit+context are provided; best-effort (won't crash if comment posting fails)\n- **AC6**: API key passed only via `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` env var (never in command string); redacted from error comments via `sanitizeOutput()`\n- 29 new tests covering all acceptance criteria\n- All 76 tests passing, typecheck and lint clean","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"cab57a4f-e8df-4648-9c51-7e23a35b2ad7","total_cost_usd":2.430533,"usage":{"input_tokens":39,"cache_creation_input_tokens":55006,"cache_read_input_tokens":2117571,"output_tokens":15143,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":55006,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":53,"outputTokens":20313,"cacheReadInputTokens":2459113,"cacheCreationInputTokens":98841,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":2.35540275,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":55654,"outputTokens":16